Welcome to the LMMS documentation Wiki. Here you find lot of information related to LMMS. 

LMMS aims to be a free alternative to popular (but commercial and closed-source) programs like FL Studio, Cubase and Logic giving you the ability of producing music with your computer by creating/synthesizing sounds, arranging samples, playing live with your keyboard and much more... LMMS combines the features of a complete tracker-/sequencer-program (pattern-/channel-/sample-/song-/effect-management) and those of powerful synthesizers and samplers in a modern, user-friendly and easy to use graphical user-interface.


